<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <%- include('../partials/head') %>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="jumbotron">
                <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center h-100">
                    <div class="col-md-9 col-lg-6 col-xl-5 order-md-2 div-2">
                        <img src="/image/home-img.png" class="img-fluid rounded-pill home-img" alt="home image">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-8 col-lg-6 col-xl-4 order-md-1 div-1 home-title-content">
                        <h2 class="home-title">Find your <span class="home-title-specific">best helpmate</span></h2>
                        <h6 class="home-subtitle">Use companion finder for their pet sitting needs</h6>
                        <p class="find-sitter-area"><a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg find-companion-btn" href="/list/listsitterpost"
                                role="button">Find a companion</a></p>
                        <a href="/list/listpetpost" class="home-find-job-link">Are you a pet sitter looking for work?</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row how-works-area">
                <div class="row g-4 how-works-content">
                    <h2 class="home-title-2">Here’s how it works</h2>
                    <div class="row justify-content-md-center">
                        <div class="col-md-auto">
                            <div class="card step-card">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <img src="/image/point-1.png"><span class="point-title">Tell us your
                                        needs</span></img>
                                    <p class="card-text step-text">What are you looking for by using filter to select
                                        your requirement.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-auto">
                            <div class="card step-card">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <img src="/image/point-2.png"><span class="point-title">Browse your
                                        matches</span></img>
                                    <p class="card-text step-text">Compare pet sitters and prices, then talk to the ones
                                        you like.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-auto">
                            <div class="card step-card">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <img src="/image/point-3.png"><span class="point-title">Hire the pet
                                        sitter</span></img>
                                    <p class="card-text step-text">Schedule a time with the petsitter of your choice and
                                        you’re good to go.
                                        It’s that easy.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row justify-content-md-center">
                            <div class="col-md-auto">
                                <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg get-start-btn" href="/list/listsitterpost" role="button">Get Started</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row gy-6">
                <h2 class="recommendations-title">Pet Sitter Recommendations</h2>
                <div class="row g-4 recommendations-area">
                    <div class="row recommendations-content h-100 justify-content-md-center">
                        <div class="recommendations-card-area">
                            <div id="inam" class="carousel slide carousel-dark" data-interval="false">
                                <div class="carousel-inner">
                                    <% var counter=0 %>
                                  <% data.forEach(item=>{%>
                                    <% counter++ %>
                                    <% if (counter % 3==1) { %>
                                    <div class="carousel-item <% if (counter == 1) { %>active<% } %>">
                                        <div class="container d-block">
                                            <div class="row card-row">
                                            <% } %>
                                                <div class="col-sm-6 card-col recommendations-card-col">
                                                    <div class="card recommendations-card">
                                                        <div class="card-body recommendations-card-content">
                                                            <img src="<%= item.profile.avatar%>" alt="" class="card-img recommendations-card-img">
                                                            <h4 class="card-title recommendations-card-name" id=""><%= item.profile.name %></h4>
                                                            <h5 class="card-text recommendations-card-location"><%= item.profile.city %>&#44; <%= item.profile.province %></h5>
                                                            <h6 class="card-text recommendations-card-desc-title">About me</h6>
                                                            <p class="card-text recommendations-card-desc"><%= item.profile.aboutMe %></p>
                                                                <a href="/postinfo/sitterlist/<%= item._id%>"
                                                                    class="btn recommendations-card-btn">Read
                                                                    more</a>
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                                <% if (counter % 3 == 0 || item == data.length - 1) { %>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <% } %>
                                    <%})%>
                                </div>
                                <!-- btn for prev and next -->
                                <a href="#inam" class="carousel-control-prev home-prev" data-bs-slide="prev">
                                    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon"></span>
                                </a>
                                <a href="#inam" class="carousel-control-next home-next" data-bs-slide="next">
                                    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon"></span>
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="row g-4">
                    <h2 class="about-us-title" id="about">ABOUT US</h2>
                    <div class="row g-2">
                        <div class="col h-100 about-content-area">
                            <p class="about-us-content">
                                Welcome to our pet-sitting website! We are a team of four web development students from
                                VCC who are passionate about creating websites that make a difference in
                                people's lives. Our team consists of Gina and Nicole, who are experienced in HTML, CSS
                                and user experience design and Jessica and Melody, who specialize in JavaScript and
                                database management.<br>
                                <br>
                                Our motivation for creating this website came from our shared love of pets and our
                                desire to make pet-sitting services more accessible and convenient for pet owners. We
                                understand that finding a reliable and trustworthy pet sitter can be difficult, so we
                                wanted to create a website that simplifies the process and makes it easier for pet
                                owners to connect with pet sitters in their area.<br>
                                <br>
                                Through our collaboration, we've created a user-friendly website that allows pet owners
                                to search for local pet sitters based on their location, availability, and specific pet
                                care needs. Our HTML, CSS and user experience design expertise ensures that the website
                                is visually appealing and easy to navigate, also the website is easy to use and provides
                                a positive user experience for both pet owners and pet sitters. Our JavaScript and
                                database management expertise ensures that the website is responsive and interactive and
                                all data is secure and organized.<br>
                                <br>
                                We are dedicated to providing the best possible service for both pet owners and pet
                                sitters, and we believe that our website can make a real difference in the lives of pets
                                and their owners. For any inquiries or to learn more about our website, please click
                                "contact us" that send your message to us. Thank you for browsing our pet-sitting
                                website!
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>